(57316, 1, 603, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well fought, $Gbrother:sister;! You\'ve begun your rise to the top!\n\nBut keep up with your training and stay ready. In Maldraxxus, there is always a challenger waiting to take your place.', 36753), -- -Unknown-
