(58095, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A spectacular show, Maw Walker.', 36753), -- -Unknown-
(60252, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This memory glass is old, very old. It may be the memory of a soul that moved on many years ago, we can never be certain. What is known is that the knowledge contained within can never be replicated, and soon, will never be seen again.\n\nI will immediately get to work in preserving what of it I can. I must ask that you take your leave now, please choose a suitably rich reward for your efforts.', 36753), -- -Unknown-
(60242, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, quite a find, we rarely get a glimpse into the mechanisms by which the House of Rituals enact their dark designs. I am eager to delve into this tome, purely in the interests of knowledge of course.\n\nYou may choose from some of our procured items as a reward.', 36753), -- -Unknown-
(63059, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'With more work, we can establish portals to other necropoli around the Shadowlands.', 36753), -- -Unknown-
