(60049, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done. Emeni and her constructs will make for powerful allies.\n\nThey will, however, need your assistance to reach their full potential.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
(58727, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This spot will do great for us. We can build new constructs, and a home for ourselves.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
(58671, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We make a good team, $n.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
