(62189, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh, wow, this is a real find you have. Here, a heap of Infused Rubies for the bundle, the best you will see here in the ward. And if you see one of my goods you might like, let me know.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
