(57691, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well, you are quite resourceful. Give me twenty five of your kind and some proper gear and we could defeat the Master.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
(57690, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I recognize you. Azeroth has been very busy lately, and her champions have been very much at the forefront of events. We must talk as soon as time allows.', 36734), -- -Unknown-
