(60175, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mmmm, it smells just like how I remember it! Maybe a little stale, but you won\'t hear me complaining about a job well done!', 37474), -- -Unknown-
(62453, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You know I appreciate hard work, but it\'s important to take care of yourself from time to time. Hope you had fun, blew off some steam, and are ready to get back at it!', 37474), -- -Unknown-
(60158, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It seems our partnership has become rather permanent. Cartel Ve will not rest until we are both eliminated.\n\nI suppose now would be the time to share one of my most important rules with you.', 37474), -- -Unknown-
(63154, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'An interesting artifact indeed, Maw Walker.\n\n<Ve\'nari gently taps the armor.>\n\nYou can almost hear the screams of the souls who were consumed to forge it.', 37474), -- -Unknown-
(62425, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have shown rare bravery, $n. For this the forest recognizes you. Let all know your ferocity in defending our borders, and the love you have for our charges.', 37474), -- -Unknown-
